{"comments":"LineHeight - vertical rhythm and text leading.\n\nA unitless ratio relative to font size:\n- **1.0**: Lines touch (no leading) - display text only\n- **1.2-1.3**: Tight - headings, short bursts\n- **1.4-1.5**: Normal - balanced readability\n- **1.6-1.8**: Relaxed - body text, long-form reading\n- **2.0+**: Loose - special effects, dramatic spacing\n\nLine height = font-size × ratio. For 16px text at 1.5 ratio = 24px lines.\n\nProfessional typographers call the space between lines \"leading\" (rhymes\nwith \"bedding\"), from the lead strips inserted between lines of metal type.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","LineHeight"],"LineHeight"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[79,46],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/LineHeight.purs","start":[79,1]},"title":"eqLineHeight"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","LineHeight"],"LineHeight"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[80,48],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/LineHeight.purs","start":[80,1]},"title":"ordLineHeight"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Typography","LineHeight"],"LineHeight"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[83,31],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Typography/LineHeight.purs","start":[82,1]},"title":"showLineHeight"}],"comments":"Li